p - Accessibility Services wants to help support you in your efforts to provide accessible content. In order to help you with your specific video, Accessibility Services may ask for the Kaltura ID. You can find this ID in several places. The Kaltura ID is a number or letter followed by an underscore and eight more numbers and letters (example: 1_3wsu3c5t)
p - If you open the video in video.byui.edu, the Kaltura ID will be at the end of the URL in your address bar.
